sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant I as CommandInvoker
    participant D as DepositCommand
    participant W as WithdrawCommand
    participant A as BankAccount

    C->>I: run(DepositCommand(account, 100))
    I->>D: execute()
    D->>A: credit(100)
    I->>I: history.push(DepositCommand)

    C->>I: run(WithdrawCommand(account, 50))
    I->>W: execute()
    W->>A: debit(50)
    I->>I: history.push(WithdrawCommand)

    Note over C,A: Balance: 50

    C->>I: undoLast()
    I->>W: undo()
    W->>A: credit(50)
    I->>I: history.pop()

    Note over C,A: Balance: 100 (restored)

    Note over I: Also supports: schedule, replay, audit
